<p>â€œThe surface to meaning and meaning to surface full cycle of language processingâ€ offered by the Language and Information Processing (LIPS) Research Lab distinguishes us from other research groups in the field, most of which focus on subproblems of human language processing.</p>

<p>We have experience in developing solutions and systems capable of addressing the whole spectrum of issues starting with word detection to deep semantic processing and from discourse planning and micro-planning to lexical generation. The lab broadly addresses text retrieval aspects as part of our mission.</p>

